    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cylindrical containers, usually wooden, with slightly bulging sides made of staves hooped together, and with flat, parallel ends.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
